io.github.prolobjectlink

Interface Platform

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    LoggerInterface, PlatformConsole, PrologProgrammer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPlatform, AbstractProgrammer, Backup, PlatformLogger, RemoteDatabaseServer, Restore, Tool

    public interface Platform
    Represent the platform where the system is running. The platform meanings is the application architecture stack until java virtual machine runtime. The stacked architecture elements are Operating System (OS) and Java Virtual Machine (JVM).
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jose Zalacain
